<p>as far as the tops of the flames are concerned.</p>
<p>Was pleased to find that I felt cool this morning on the road, although naturally one gets very anxious.  The main thing is to be sure that the effect finishes with the end of the danger.</p>
<p>Heard a piano going in one of the houses occupied by Australian pioneers.  What next I wonder!</p>
<p>Bandaged a sprained wrist for a talkative French soldier this afternoon.  We are great plans with our French neighbours.</p>
